verbose_text: Complex assembly is triggered by molecular cues from pathogenic and commensal microorganisms (e.g., nucleic acids, bacterial secretion apparatuses, flagellins, and toxins) as well as sterile danger signals and particulates including, ATP, alum adjuvants, and gout associated uric acid crystals.
